513
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:35,021
but when you're at the point where you want to shoot someone,

514
00:26:35,072 --> 00:26:36,650
you want to take them down, you don't want to wing 'em.

515
00:26:38,016 --> 00:26:39,404
Heart and head --

516
