that's where it counts.

517
00:26:41,356 --> 00:26:42,275
Ain't that the truth?

518
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:47,345
You need focus, precision, the ability to only think about the task at hand.

519
00:26:47,892 --> 00:26:49,762
When I'm working, my family doesn't exist.

520
00:26:50,504 --> 00:26:51,353
That sound awful?

521
00:26:51,491 --> 00:26:52,422
No.

522
00:26:52,929 --> 00:26:53,669
It's not.

523
00:26:54,139 --> 00:26:56,425
Because when I'm with my family, work doesn't exist.

524
00:26:59,769 --> 00:27:02,606
I think my father has a similar philosophy.

525
00:27:03,273 --> 00:27:04,895
Of course, he's a murderer, so...

526
00:27:05,534 --> 00:27:06,527
yeah.

527
00:27:09,334 --> 00:27:10,107
Yeah.

528
00:27:13,523 --> 00:27:15,930
Hey, we should have some chicks over tomorrow night.

529
00:27:16,188 --> 00:27:18,272
Dad's got this banquet at the Neptune grand,

530
00:27:18,323 --> 00:27:20,036
